item.description:

[quote=“Javacisnotrecognized, post:4, topic:53270”][quote author=mumakilspawn link=topic=75083.msg841673#msg841673 date=1170143133]

127.0.0.1. If you can’t get admin there, then you suck at life.

thats the default server dumpy dumpy. The man needs some help. DOnt plat it off.
[/quote]

Retard, 127.0.0.1 connects to the computer that is making the connection. If you can’t get administrator on your OWN server, which involves little more than changing “playyerrights = 3”, then you suck at life. Although I find it hard to believe that you wouldn’t already know you suck at life.[/quote]
He said “ON” ur server dumbass
